## Overview

Welcome to the AI for Networking and Security Engineers course! This first volume establishes the core concepts you'll need to effectively apply AI and Large Language Models (LLMs) to networking and security operations.

### What You'll Learn

- **Generative AI Fundamentals**: Understanding how LLMs work and their capabilities
