## Strategy 2: Intelligent Model Routing

### The 80/15/5 Rule

- **80% of requests**: Simple tasks → Use cheap models (Haiku, GPT-4o-mini)
- **15% of requests**: Moderate complexity → Use mid-tier (Sonnet, GPT-4o)
- **5% of requests**: Complex reasoning → Use premium (Opus, o1)

### Cost Comparison

| Task | Wrong Model | Right Model | Savings |
|------|-------------|-------------|---------|
| Log classification | Opus ($0.045) | Haiku ($0.0008) | 98% |
| Config review | Opus ($0.089) | Sonnet ($0.025) | 72% |
| BGP troubleshooting | Haiku ($0.002) | Sonnet ($0.025) | -92% (worse quality) |

### ModelRouter Implementation

